you are designing a laptop
with the help of your brain.

00:17:58.720 --> 00:18:01.360
Unfortunately with us what is
when you study the brain

00:18:01.360 --> 00:18:04.800
you are studying the organ
with the help of the same organ.

00:18:04.800 --> 00:18:07.200
So we are studying the brain
with the help of the human brain

00:18:07.200 --> 00:18:09.440
because everything is human brain
at the end of the day.

00:18:09.440 --> 00:18:16.000
