00:19:10.480 --> 00:19:12.720
It is basically the resting state.

00:19:12.720 --> 00:19:16.960
If you are just sitting, walking,
not doing anything consciously

00:19:16.960 --> 00:19:20.080
as we call it, that is your
default mode network.

00:19:20.080 --> 00:19:22.080
You might say it is kind of
the background of something

00:19:22.080 --> 00:19:23.840
that your brain exists in.

00:19:23.840 --> 00:19:28.000
As soon as you start changing
your conscious effort from that

00:19:28.000 --> 00:19:31.680
to a focused action
to a concentrated action

00:19:31.680 --> 00:19:35.760
