00:19:35.760 --> 00:19:38.560
thinking about something
in very specific terms.

00:19:38.560 --> 00:19:42.320
So that shifts your focus
from the default mode network

00:19:42.320 --> 00:19:45.760
to a more conscious effort.

00:19:45.760 --> 00:19:47.680
That is a shift in consciousness.

00:19:47.680 --> 00:19:52.080
